# CMM3 PDCA: ONCE v0.3.21.2 - Component Refactor Preserving Working Code

**Component**: ONCE v0.3.21.2  
**Date**: 2025-11-19 UTC 17:30  
**Author**: AI Assistant (Claude Sonnet 4.5)  
**PDCA Type**: Pragmatic Refactoring with Component Separation  
**Parent Version**: 0.3.21.1  
